sub_title: International metric-driven B2B Marketing Leader in Information technology
summary: Experienced Director of Global Marketing with a demonstrated experience in the information services industry. Strong marketing professional with skills in Global Team leadership, Demand Creation, Digital & Web Marketing and Thought Leadership, Paid Search and Paid Social, Account-Based Marketing, Content Marketing, Change Management, Marketing Management, Event Management, Market Research, and Multi-touch and Nurture Marketing Campaigns. Passion for Cultural Awareness, Inclusion and Diversity. Driven by measuring ROI on marketing and supporting YOY growth.
